<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Music Theory</h1>

<blockquote class="border-l-4 border-gray-300 pl-4 py-2 my-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">This page explains <strong class="font-semibold">background concepts that couldn't fit in popups</strong>, written in guitarist-friendly language.  </blockquote>
<blockquote class="border-l-4 border-gray-300 pl-4 py-2 my-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Each section ends with a <strong class="font-semibold">30-second recipe</strong> for immediate hands-on practice.  </blockquote>
<blockquote class="border-l-4 border-gray-300 pl-4 py-2 my-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Designed to be fully understood <strong class="font-semibold">through text alone</strong>, no images or audio needed.</blockquote>

<hr class="my-8 border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600" />

